f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T23:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd8691ea1054f15db33e071253079286f7c50a4","tid":2339653,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:01:12.000Z","msg":"哈哈 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b077bb54e0c0e25484f2bd82e8509f96d38d062e","tid":2339653,"uid":365618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T00:14:28.000Z","msg":"樓主睇開啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如諗吓本身嗰一百萬都唔係屬於你嘅，既然而家更加了解伯母為人係點，不如當係一個機會斷絕來往囉"},{"pid":"484c87cb2db31659595653b80c2fb58bd0ac1d0b","tid":2339653,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"呃人投資嘅仆街死之外，根本成件事係石頭腳，<br />\n老母廢你一早知，你咁樣畀佢揸旗實出事。"},{"pid":"14b45895750e812aee784a914b7643873c9e88fb","tid":2339653,"uid":156121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"屋企人老左 D錢一定係自己拎<br />\n保重"},{"pid":"0bbb7a6492f023016518c1f8a9db8edd08f17341","tid":2339653,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d453a473c056dd2e777a86df13760fa3ceebf9","tid":2339653,"uid":244845,"like":2,"dislike":37,"score":-35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T22:04:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲事你唔可以怪曬佢<br />\n當然你可能覺得你老母好撚on9好蠢 下刪一萬字<br />\n不過當人寂寞/孤獨起上黎 就好易有啲咩冇理性既情況<br />\n而家有個「男人」關心佢 比到咁多年佢想要既野佢<br />\n佢緊既底褲都唔要比埋人<br />\n咁呢件事最好係你兩個傾下先<br />\n提下佢 佢地咁耐冇咁 比曬啲錢人會有啲危險（好語氣）<br />\n同埋你可以講下 作為做仔 你都希望佢開心<br />\n不如你（樓豬）同埋個男人見下面先 之類之類<br />\n總知唔好一黎斬頭話佢蠢呀 呢樣個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hk